@{PARD}
@{B}Silent Death Description:@{UB}@{PAR}

Silent death is an intelligent piece of swamp that can change appearance and
inner structure to either cause a creature to fall fast to its death, or permit
passing over without falling through. It's hard to see, hard to recognize, and
hard to re-locate.@{PAR}

