@{PARD}
@{B}Silent Death Habitat/Society:@{UB}@{PAR}

Solitary, thinking food-oriented. However, with size its powers increase,
permitting communication with others of its kind. Also, the scope of interests
widens with intelligence, and one may converse with other races, too.@{PAR}

@ENDNODE

